title: Pacific Seafood is currently seeking a Class A Driver.
text:
Pacific Seafood is currently seeking a Class A Driver. ad date: 10/10/2015 
Pacific Seafood is currently seeking a Class A Driver. Requires a Class A CDL and prior experience in transporting refrigerated and frozen food products is preferred. Full benefit package. Pre-employment screening required. EEO Company. For more information or to apply visit www.pacseafood.com or send resume to Pacific Seafood, Attn: HR, P.O. Box 97, Clackamas, OR 97015.
